title: Kate Moss ‘blacklists’ supermodel BFF Cara Delevingne | The
text:
THEY are supermodel BFFs but it appears that Kate Moss has turned on Cara Delevingne with reports she has ‘black-listed’ her former friend.
The Sun reports that Delevingne, 22, has fallen foul of Moss, 41, after the younger model left the agency that reps them both to pursue her acting career.
Happier times ... Cara Delevingne and Kate Moss laugh together. Picture: Splash Source: Supplied
Delevingne has been modelling’s ‘it girl’ for awhile now but has made it clear she wants to branch into acting, having filmed roles in Paper Towns, Pan and Suicide Squad .
“Kate has black-listed Cara now. It’s very unfortunate and hopefully might be a temporary thing, but they’re definitely not friends at the moment,” a source told The Sun . “Kate wasn’t happy with Cara’s clash with Naomi and felt she should have treated her with more respect.”
But The Sun also suggests that Delevingne had a row with Moss’ long-time friend, Naomi Campbell, in March over her treatment of mutual friend, Rihanna.
“Naomi accused Cara of ‘disrespecting’ Rihanna and started yelling, before Naomi pushed Cara, who pushed back. Cara pulled Naomi’s weave, but it didn’t come off,” the source said.
Campbell took to her Twitter page to deny that she had fallen out with Delevingne, while her reps said “no fight took place between Naomi Campbell and Cara Delevingne at Paris club Castel.”
Friends for years ... Kate Moss and Naomi Campbell. Picture: Supplied Source: Supplied
They go way back ... Naomi Campbell and Kate Moss in 1998. Picture: AP Source: AP
Moss and Delevingne have worked together on campaigns including Burberry and in May were unveiled as the faces of Mango.
“This is the first time I have worked with Mango and having Kate as my partner in crime is ideal! We are a lethal combination,” Delevingne said at the time. “I admire her personally and professionally, she represents a true fashion icon. It is a privilege to learn and to share this experience with her. The shoot has been epic, it’s always fun when Miss Moss is around.”
Colleagues ... Cara Delevingne and Kate Moss are the joint face of Mango. Picture: Splash Source: Supplied
Moss has been equally as gushing in the past about Delevingne.
“Cara’s got it — she doesn’t need advice, she knows what she is doing, she’s very confident in front of the camera,” she said. “She’s a great model.”
Moss recently announced that her and husband of four years, Jamie Hince, have split up.
Delevingne is currently dating singer St Vincent.
Originally published as Moss ‘blacklists’ supermodel BFF
